@startuml
title LongConspectWriter - pipeline state diagram

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> Created
Created --> ConfigLoaded : load_configs()
ConfigLoaded --> InputValidated : input file exists
ConfigLoaded --> Failed : config read error
InputValidated --> Transcribing : action=all or stt
InputValidated --> SingleStageRunning : individual action
InputValidated --> Failed : input path missing

Transcribing --> TranscriptReady : raw transcript saved
TranscriptReady --> Drafting : _call_drafter()
Drafting --> DraftReady : cleaned transcript saved
DraftReady --> LocalClustering : _call_local_clustering()
LocalClustering --> LocalClustersReady : local clusters saved
LocalClustersReady --> LocalPlanning : _call_local_planner()
LocalPlanning --> LocalPlanReady : local topics saved
LocalPlanReady --> GlobalPlanning : _call_global_planner()
GlobalPlanning --> GlobalPlanReady : chapter plan saved
GlobalPlanReady --> GlobalClustering : _call_global_clustering()
GlobalClustering --> GlobalClustersReady : clusters attached to chapters
GlobalClustersReady --> Synthesizing : _call_synthesizer()
Synthesizing --> JsonConspectReady : JSON conspect saved
JsonConspectReady --> ExportingMarkdown : convert_json_to_md()
ExportingMarkdown --> MarkdownReady : Markdown saved
MarkdownReady --> Completed

SingleStageRunning --> SingleArtifactReady : selected stage saved artifact
SingleArtifactReady --> Completed

Transcribing --> Failed : STT process error
Drafting --> Failed : LLM generation error
LocalClustering --> Failed : clustering error
LocalPlanning --> Failed : LLM generation error
GlobalPlanning --> Failed : invalid JSON plan
GlobalClustering --> Failed : matching error
Synthesizing --> Failed : synthesis error
ExportingMarkdown --> Failed : export error
SingleStageRunning --> Failed : stage error

Completed --> [*]
Failed --> [*]

@enduml
